                    <small class="font-semibold text-start flex items-center gap-x-2"><Check class="size-5 fill-[#00D47E] text-black" aria-hidden="true"/> Experienced for more than 10 years</small>
                    <small class="font-semibold text-start flex items-center gap-x-2"><Check class="size-5 fill-[#00D47E] text-black" aria-hidden="true"/> Support for the latest technology</small>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="content flex flex-col gap-4">
                <p class="text-start text-sm font-semibold text-pretty">By increasing the effectiveness and efficiency of electricity use, the use of renewable resources is very profitable for all industrial services</p>
                <div class="btn-footer mt-3">
                    <a class="px-6 py-3 bg-white text-black rounded-3xl" href="/" aria-label="Get in touch" role="button">
                        Get in touch <ArrowUp class="inline-block ml-2" aria-hidden="true" />
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-nav flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center py-4">

